title: Compression Crimp RCA Yellow
blurb:
Use these RCA Crimp connectors for high end audio and video you need to use, high quality connectors.  Recommended for Pay TV, HDTV, Component and RGB. Use in conjunction with TH1802 crimping tool. Comes in Red, Blue, Green, White and Yellow
PP-0200           Red
PP-0201           Blue
PP-0202           Green
PP-0203           White
PP-0204           Yellow
